    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In Medieval Spain, individuals who were in charge of overseeing construction works, either as master builders or master masons.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
